import React,{useEffect, useRef, useState} from 'react' import axios from 'axios' function Form(){ const [reasons, setReasons] = useState(new Array()); useEffect(()=>{ axios.get('http://localhost:8081/') .then((res)=>{ setReasons(res.data); }) .catch((err)=>console.log(err)); },[]); const [isSatisfied, setSatisfied] = useState(false); const satisfied = useRef() const select = (e)=>{ e.preventDefault(); const selected = satisfied.current.value; selected === 'Y'?setSatisfied(true):setSatisfied(false); } return(
{isSatisfied?
    {reasons.map((reason)=>{ console.log(reason.code);
  • {reason.desc}
    • })}
:null}
); } export default Form;
